            </div>

            <div class="col">
                <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <div class="card-footer bg-white border-0 p-0">
                            <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                                <img src="~/images/avatar2.png" alt="Reviewer" class="rounded-circle me-3" style="width: 50px; height: 50px; object-fit: cover;" />
                                <div>
                                    <h6 class="fw-bold mb-0">JEREMY VOLKOV</h6>
                                    <small class="text-muted">CEO</small>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mb-2 text-warning">★ ★ ★ ★ ★</div>
                        <p class="card-text">“We’ve been using this company for our office stationery needs for over a year, and they never let us down. Their warehouse is well-organized, and orders are always accurate. The automated stock updates save us so much time.”</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col">
                <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <div class="card-footer bg-white border-0 p-0">
                            <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                                <img src="~/images/avatar3.png" alt="Reviewer" class="rounded-circle me-3" style="width: 50px; height: 50px; object-fit: cover;" />
                                <div>
                                    <h6 class="fw-bold mb-0">BRANDON KING</h6>
                                    <small class="text-muted">ASSISTANT</small>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mb-2 text-warning">★ ★ ★ ★ ★</div>
                        <p class="card-text">“Reliable, efficient, and professional! Their storage and order management system is top-notch. We no longer waste money running out of essential supplies because their system keeps everything in check. A game-changer for our business!”</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col">
                <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <div class="card-footer bg-white border-0 p-0">
                            <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                                <img src="~/images/avatar3.png" alt="Reviewer" class="rounded-circle me-3" style="width: 50px; height: 50px; object-fit: cover;" />
                                <div>
                                    <h6 class="fw-bold mb-0">NIKOLAI SOKOLOV</h6>
                                    <small class="text-muted">SCHOOL PRINCIPAL</small>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mb-2 text-warning">★ ★ ★ ★ ★</div>
                        <p class="card-text">“Fast and flawless service every time! The streamlined ordering process and prompt deliveries make this company stand out. Their customer support is also fantastic, always ready to assist with any inquiries. Definitely our go-to supplier!”</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
